creator: Dubixstudio
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to our Chess 3D app - the ultimate chess game experience for chess enthusiasts!
With our chess game, you can enjoy playing chess from a 3D perspective, bringing the game to life like never before. Our app offers a range of play modes, including one-player and two-player chess, as well as multiplayer options, making it perfect for solo practice or challenging your friends and family to a game.

The game settings
Our app also comes with various settings options, allowing you to customize your game experience to suit your preferences. Whether you prefer a more challenging game or a more relaxed one, our app has got you covered. Do you want it to be extra challenging? Then try setting the promotion to a knight automatically. This way, your first queen will remain your only queen. To personalize your game even further, you can choose your own avatar and your opponent's avatar and customize them with your names.

What’s so special about it?
The most special part of our app is the ability to rotate the camera around the table, giving you a truly realistic feel of playing a real chess game. However, you can also switch to a 2D view if you prefer a more traditional chess game experience.

So, whether you're a beginner or a seasoned player, our Chess 3D app is the perfect choice for experiencing the excitement of real chess. Download it now and start playing!

Since we always appreciate constructive feedback, please send it to the following email address: [your email for feedback]. Our staff will take care of your request as soon as possible!
